    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/853a5d6bee04fe1964a172f63ca4d9a6.webp?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=29 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从昏迷中醒来，面前只有一块在黑暗中闪烁的屏幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全无记忆的情况下，你却被某个神秘人告知，必须立刻配合“研究所”进行一起超自然事件的调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >否则，将再也不会有醒来的可能。你只能答应，立刻开始用眼前这台“灵异设备”，投入调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/a77a48efa24c561c598b27d8de3d46c6.poster.avif?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/a77a48efa24c561c598b27d8de3d46c6.webm?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/a77a48efa24c561c598b27d8de3d46c6.mp4?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在网络上一步步积累线索，你发现，看似普通的失踪事件背后，竟然隐藏着“研究所”真正的研究目标：████。随着记忆不断涌现，一个令人不寒而栗的真相逐渐浮出水面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/2cb1126ae3a894dab462fb0f2b2da0ef.poster.avif?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/2cb1126ae3a894dab462fb0f2b2da0ef.webm?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/2cb1126ae3a894dab462fb0f2b2da0ef.mp4?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/b0f9ba3eafe5f945d4819ef40ab7157d.webp?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=29 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >影游结合：游戏采用真人拍摄视频，打造沉浸式体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多媒互动：通过观看视频、锚定灵异锚点、网络搜索、论坛互动，搜集事件线索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >情景还原：词条组合玩法，一步步还原事件发生的当时当刻。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/137cf321ecedcd593f94362fe905f6fa.poster.avif?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/137cf321ecedcd593f94362fe905f6fa.webm?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/137cf321ecedcd593f94362fe905f6fa.mp4?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/c20f16d503e8ae448081954ddbe1ac5a.poster.avif?t=1747214603\" width=616 height=125 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194070/extras/c20f16d503e8ae448081954ddbe1ac5a.webm?t=1747214603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
